race.comment: This is as good a Class 1 you'll find at Bordertown. GOLD TOPAZ (10) will be strongly fancied on his last run, when hitting the line hard for a solid fourth in Listed grade at Flemington on Melbourne Cup day. Very well placed here on that figure and should be in the finish. YOUBEEFORTY (5) was overdue for a win before scoring his maiden success at Morphettville last start when clearing right out. On speed runner off the mark now and will take caching again. STREAMELOT (12) was a close-up third two back in a maiden then struggled in the very heavy ground last time over the border. This will be much better and gets chance to atone. PALTINIAN (3) is a Class 1 horse but has been racing in the country cups in Victoria. Back to right grade and must be included.
